athletics events for the proposed new national stadium at Wembley,
British Culture, Media and Sport Secretary Chris Smith said on
Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Smith told the House of Commons he had reached the "reluctant
conclusion" the present design "cannot readily provide the central
venue for an Olympic Games bid for London".
</P>
<P>
