<HEADLINE> Shanghai and McDonald's Set Up Joint Venture </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, December 2 (Xinhua) -- Shanghai Hualian Group and the
world's largest fastfood chain McDonald's signed a contract today
to set up the Shanghai Hualian McDonald's Co.Ltd in east China.
</P>
<P>
"The economic cooperation will accelerate Shanghai's pace of
readjustment to fit into the world market," said Feng Guoqin, vice
mayor of the city in charge of business affairs.
</P>
<P>
