Whaley, senior vice-president of the International Partner
Relationship of McDonald's Co. expressed his satisfaction with the
agreement, saying that the Hualian Group is "an ideal partner."
</P>
<P>
The Hualian Group has set up over 1,200 chain stores,
supermarkets, and department stores in the past five years.
</P>
<P>
McDonald's has set up over 25,000 restaurants in 117 countries
and regions, with its trade volume standing at 36 billion U.S.
dollars in 1998.
</P>
<P>
McDonald's now has 246 fast-food restaurants in China, with 25
in Shanghai, less than the Chinese cities of Beijing, Guangzhou
and Shenzhen. 
