<TEXT>
<P>
YANTAI, December 2 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Vice-Premier Wu Bangguo
today urged people engaged in rescue operations for victims of the
Dashun shipwreck to coordinate the recovery efforts.
</P>
<P>
The ferry Dashun sank near the port city of Yantai, east China'
s Shandong Province, on November 24.
</P>
<P>
