<HEADLINE> Chinese Universities to Recruit Learners from Macao </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MACAO, December 2 (Xinhua) -- The application for Macao people'
s studying postgraduate and doctoral degrees in universities and
colleges in the inland areas of China began here today.
</P>
<P>
More than 100 institutions of higher learning in the inland
areas are recruiting learners from Macao, as well as those from
Hong Kong and Taiwan.
</P>
<P>
The application will last till the end of the month, but
organizers said that the deadline might be postponed for many
people are engaged in activities concerning Macao's return to the
motherland on December 20.
</P>
<P>
It will be the seventh time for universities and colleges in
the inland areas to admit learners for postgraduate and doctoral
degrees from Macao. The examination will be held early next year.
</P>
<P>
During the past six years, a total of 53 institutions of higher
learning in the inland areas had recruited 713 such learners from
Macao, 665 of whom were postgraduate learners.  
</P>
