<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, December 2 (Xinhua) -- Washington's hands were
not completely clean in pushing the European Union (EU) to
eliminate export subsidies for its farmers, South African Trade
and Industry Minister Alec Erwin said in Seattle Wednesday.
</P>
