<HEADLINE> Anhui Province Helping Needy People Out Of Poverty </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HEFEI, December 2 (Xinhua) -- Anhui Province had helped 600,000
of the local people get rid of poverty during the past two years,
reducing the number of local needy people to 960,000 at the end of
1998.
</P>
<P>
The annual net income for per capita in local rural areas rose
from 1,302 yuan in 1996 to 1,591 yuan in 1998.
</P>
<P>
Improvement of infrastructure in the province's 17 most-
impoverished counties resulted in better living condition for
local farmers.
</P>
<P>
Nearly one billion yuan was invested in the aid-the-poor
program in the poverty-stricken counties each year.
</P>
<P>
Another 600,000 needy people in the province are expected to
get rid of poverty the turn of the century.  
</P>
</TEXT>
