<HEADLINE> Wahid Accepts Golden Edition of "Confucian Analects" </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 2 (Xinhua) -- International Confucian
Association (ICA) presented visiting Indonesian President
Abdurrahman Wahid a golden edition of "Confucian Analects" here
this afternoon.
</P>
<P>
Wahid said at the ceremony that the exchange of the cultures of
Confucian and Islam could be dated back a long time ago. He
expressed the belief that such exchange would be further promoted
in the next century.
</P>
