the conviction at the ceremony that President Wahid's present
China visit would enhance Sino-Indonesian cooperation in various
fields.
</P>
<P>
"Confucian Analects" is one of the most important works of
Confucianism. The golden edition of the works has been permanently
preserved by the United Nations Educational, Scientific and
Cultural Organization. 
