<HEADLINE> Construction of Large Sewage Disposal Plant Completed </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TIANJIN, December 2 (Xinhua) -- Construction work on a 160-
million-yuan sewage treatment plant has been completed at the
development zone of Tianjin, the largest port city in north China.
</P>
<P>
The plant covers an area of 6.71 hectares and is able to serve
enterprises and residents in the zone by disposing 100,000 tons
sewage per day.
</P>
<P>
With world-advanced technology, the operation of the plant will
make it possible for all the sewage in the development zone to be
treated, reducing pollution to sea water and helping improve
environment and attract investment.  
