is expected the Plant will make 352 million yuan in sales by 2004
and its products will become a permament fixture in the Asian-
Pacific regional market.
</P>
<P>
Philips is one of China's major overseas investors. To date,
Philips has funded more than 20 businesses in China, with a total
investment exceeding one billion U.S. dollars.
</P>
<P>
The Xiamen company is Philips' fourth lighting electronics
plant in China. The other three are located in Shanghai.
