<HEADLINE> Tim Hardaway on Injured List with Jammed Right Knee </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, December 1 (Xinhua) -- Miami Heat star guard Tim
Hardaway, who had missed the last three games with a jammed right
knee, today was placed on the injured list.
</P>
<P>
The move was made prior to tonight's home game against the
Philadelphia 76ers. Rookie Anthony Carter started as point guard
for the fourth straight game and figures to make at least four
more starts as Hardaway will be out a minimum of five games.
</P>
