<HEADLINE> Graf to Receive Olympic Order </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GENEVA, December 1 (Xinhua) -- Retired tennis star Steffi Graf
will receive the Olympic Order presented by International Olympic
Committee (IOC) president Juan Antonio Samaranch, it was announced
by the IOC on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Graf, who retired this year after winning 22 Grand Slam titles,
will receive the award at a ceremony at the Olympic museum at
Lausanne on Monday. 
</P>
