The last two carriages of the train of the Indian Pacific
company, loaded with cars and the first carriage of the commuter
train were derailed in the collision, AAP said.
</P>
<P>
Police said all the dead were passengers on the commuter train.
</P>
<P>
The trains were evacuated and the injured were being treated at
the scene, an ambulance spokesman said. 
