final-status talks at the Neve Ilan Hotel outside Jerusalem
Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Avi Ben-Bassat, director-general of the Israeli Finance
Ministry, put three proposals for economic ties on the negotiation
table, but there was still no detailed news about the content of
these proposals, Israeli Radio reported.
